Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SALA YA JUBILEE</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baba uliye mbinguni, imani ulio tujalia katika Mwanao Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristu, kaka yetu, na mwaliwa upendo uliowashwa mioyoni </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwetu na Roho Mtakatifu, na ziamshe upia ndani </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yetu, tumaini lenye heri na ujio wa ufalme wako.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunaomba neema yako itubadilishe, ili tuwe wakulima </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wasiochoka na mbegu za injili. Mbegu hizo zibadilishe kutoka </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndani ubinadamu na ulimwengu wote, katika tarajio la </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uhakikaa la mbingu mpya na dunia mpya, pale ambapo nguvu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>za uovu zitakapokuwa zimeshindwa, utukufu wako </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utang'aa milele. Neema ya Jubilee na iamshe upya ndani yetu, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>sisi mahujaji wa matumaini, shauku ya hazina za mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neema hiyo hiyo ieneze furaha na amani ya Mwokozi</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na amani ya Mkombozi wetu duniani kote. Ewe Mungu wetu, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mbarikiwa milele, utukufu na sifa ni kwako hata milele. Amina</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
