Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nu muracaria?</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao makimucokeria atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni Yesu uria Munazari;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni nii.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Judasi, ucio wamukunyaniire,
 o nake ni aarungii hamwe nao. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>O aakimera uguo ati ni Nii, magicoka na thutha, makigua thii. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Akimoria ringi:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nu muracaria?</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Makiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni Yesu uria Munazari.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni ndamuira ati ni nii; akoruo ni nii mugucaragia, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>no kirekei aya  aya methiire.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na nigetha kiugo kihingio, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kiria oigire ati andu  aria uheete gutiri o na umwe ndateire. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Simoni Petero, tondu aari na ruhio rua njora </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agikirucomora, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agiikia ngombo ya Muthinjiri-Ngai uria munene, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akimitinia gutu kwa urio. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri, ngombo io yetagwo Maliku. Nake Yesu akiira Petero atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Cokia ruhio njora-ini; gikombe kiria ithe witu aheete, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndige gukinyuira?</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nayo mbutu ya thigari na munene wayo, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o na makanga ma Ayahudi, magikinyita Yesu makimuoha, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>makiamba kumutwara kwa Anasi, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni gukuruo ni we wari muthoni wa Kaifa, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uria waari Muthinjiri-Ngai munene mwaka ucio. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri, ucio Kaifa ni uria wa taarire Ayahudi akiuga atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wega no mundu umwe akuire kirindi. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Simoni Petero akirumirira Yesu, o na murutwo ungi nake. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri, murutwo ucio ungi ni oio ni Muthinjiri-Ngai ucio munene; </s></f>"},{ID:24,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>indi Petero agitigwo arungii muromo-ini na ndatonye. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake murutwo ucio ungi, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ucio woio ni Muthinjiri-Ngai ucio munene akiuma akiariria muikaria wa muromo , </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agotonyia Petero. Nake muiritu ucio waikaragia muromo agikiira Petero atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kai we nawe uri murutwo wa mundu uyu?</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Petero akiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aca ni ndiri wake.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri ngombo cia kuu, na makanga, ni kurugama marugamite, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maakitie mwaki wa makara, tondu kwari na heho, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na ni guota motaga mwaki ucio. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Petero o nake aari hamwe nao, akarugama agota mwaki. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Muthinjiri-Ngai uria munene agikiuria uhoro wa arutwo ake na </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wa maundu maria aarutanaga. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu akimucokeria atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nii-ri, nduire njaragiria kirindi hatari hitho; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hingo ciothe ndirarutagira andu uhoro mathunagogi, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o na hekaru-ini, o haria Ayahudi othe monganagira; </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na ndiri undu ndanoiga na ngungui. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nii wanjuria ni undu ki? Ta kiurie aria maanaigua, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uria ndamerire; nio moi maundu maria ndoigire.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Oiga uguo, mundu umwe wa makanga warungii </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hoo akigutha Yesu na ruhi, akiuga atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Niguo wacokeria Muthinjiri-Ngai uria munene?</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu akimucokeria atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ongoruo ni uuru ndoiga, onania uuru ucio. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na ongoruo ni ndoiga wega, wakinguthira ki?</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake anasi agikiuga atwaruo gwa Kaifa, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Muthinjiri-Ngai uria munene, atwaruo ari o muohe. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri, Simoni Petero ni kurugama arugamite agiota mwaki. </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Agikiurio atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Anga wee nawe uri murutwo wake?</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Agikaana akiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aca ndiri wake.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nayo ngombo imwe ya Muthinjiri-Ngai uria munene, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na yari ya kwa uria watinirio gutu ni Petero akiuria,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Githii nii ndikuonire mwi nake haria mugunda-ini?</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Petero agikana ringi; na kahinda okau nguku ikigamba. </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu magikimuumia kwa Kaifa makimutwara nyumbaini iria ya guciriruo, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na nii rucini tene; nao ene matiigana </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>gutonya nyumba io ya guciriruo thiini, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>matokagwatwo ni thahu, no mahote kuria Bathika. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondu ucio Pilato akiuma njaa kuu maari, akiuria,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mundu ucio-ri, muramuthitakira ki?</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Magicokia makimuira atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Koruo mundu ucio ti mwikinai-ri, ni tungiakimurehe kuri wee?</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato agikimera,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mutikimutware, inyui ene mukamutuire cira kuringana na mawatho manyu.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao Ayahudi makimuira atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ithui tutire na rutha rwa kuuragithia mundu.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na ni getha kiugo kia Yesu kihingio, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kiria oigire akiorota gukua kuria agakua. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondu wa uguo-ri, Pilato agicoka nyumba-ini ya guciriruo, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agiita Yesu akimuuria,</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wee uri muthamaki wa Ayahudi?</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ukuuria uguo wiritwo ni ngoro yaku mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kana ni andu angi makwirire uhoro wakwa?</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kai ndii Muyahudi nii? Anga ti ruriri rwanyu na Athinjiri-Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>aria anene makuneana kuri nii; ni atia wikite?</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Yesu agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uthamaki wakwa ti wa guku thi; uthamaki wakwa ungiri wa guku thi, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>andu akwa mangiri kuruta mbaara, ndikaneo Ayahudi; </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>no riri, uria kuri, uthamaki wakwa ti wa guku.</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondu ucio Pilato akimuria atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Anga ukiri o Muthamaki wee?</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Yesu agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>We ni woiga, amu ndi Muthamaki. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nikio ndaciariruo na nikio njukite guku thi, </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ati nduike muira wa uhoro uria wa ma. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uhoro uria wa ma-ri, mundu o wothe waguo ni aiguaga mugambo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato akimuuria atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uhoro uria wa ma ukiri uriku?</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aarikia kuuga uguo, akiuma njaa ringi kuri Ayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akimeera atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nii-ri, ndikuona uuru ekite o na uriku. </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>No mwina mutugo, ati hindi ya Bathika ngamuohorera </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mundu umwe: riu-ri, mwenda ndimuohorere Muthamaki wa Ayahudi?</s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao magiitika ringi kwanirira makiugaga atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ndukaohore uyu, ohora Baraba!</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Na riri, baraba ucio ari mutunyani. </s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hindi io Pilato agigicoka agitwara Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akimuhurithia na kiboko kiri njaga. </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nacio thigari igituma thumbi ya miigua, </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ikimuikira mutwe, na ikimuhumba nguo ndune ya rangi ta wa ndathi; </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>igokaga hari we, ikoiga,</s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wi muhoro Muthamaki wa Ayahudi!</s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ikamugutha na hi. Nake Pilato akiuma njaa ringi, akimera atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Oneni, ngumuumiria haha muri, </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mumenye ndikuona ngero agerete o na iriku.</s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Yesu nake agikiuma nja e na thumbi io ya miigua ona nguo io ndune. </s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato akimera atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Rorei mundu ni uyu!</s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Athinjiri-Ngai aria anene o na makanga makimuona, </s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>makirika kuanirira, makiugaga:</s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mwambithie muti iguru! mwambithie muti iguru.</s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato akimera atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mutikimutware inyuene, mumwambe muti iguru! </s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>amu nii ndinaona ngero agerete.</s></f>"},{ID:111,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao Ayahudi makimucokera atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:112,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ithui turi na watho witu na tundu wa watho ucio ni </s></f>"},{ID:113,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kuuragwo agiiriruo kuuragwo, tondu ni etuite Muru wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:114,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Pilato akiigua uhoro ucio akiya gwitigira kwi uria egwitigirite, </s></f>"},{ID:115,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agitonya nyumba iria ya giciriruo, akiuria Yesu atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:116,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uri wa kuu we?</s></f>"},{ID:117,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>No riri, Yesu ndaigana kumucokeria atiriri:</s></f>"},{ID:118,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondu ucio Pilato akimuuria:</s></f>"},{ID:119,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kai ungirega kunjariria? Kai utoi ndi na hinya njuge </s></f>"},{ID:120,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wohoruo na ndi na hinya njuge wambwo muti iguru?</s></f>"},{ID:121,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu akimucokeria akimuira atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:122,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ndungiri na hinya unjike undu o na uriku, </s></f>"},{ID:123,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>utangehereeruo iguru; na tondu ucio, uria wihitie </s></f>"},{ID:124,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>muno ni uria uneanire kuri wee.</s></f>"},{ID:125,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aaigua uguo, Pilato akienda amuohere, indi </s></f>"},{ID:126,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ayahudi makianirira, makiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:127,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wohora mundu uyu-ri, nduri murata wa Kaisari. </s></f>"},{ID:128,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mundu wothe wituaga Muthamaki ni amenete Kaisari.</s></f>"},{ID:129,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Pilato aakiugwa uhoro ucio, agitwara Yesu nja, </s></f>"},{ID:130,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agiikarira giti gia utuiro, handu hetagwo haria-</s></f>"},{ID:131,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>haare-mahiga, na hakigwetwo na Kihibrania </s></f>"},{ID:132,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hagetwo Gabatha. na riri, kwari muthenya wa </s></f>"},{ID:133,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ihaariria  ria Bathika na gugakinya ta thaa thita. Akiira Ayahudi,</s></f>"},{ID:134,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni uyu, Muthamaki wanyu!</s></f>"},{ID:135,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao magikianiriira makiuga,</s></f>"},{ID:136,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni atwaruo!ni atwaruo! mwambithie muti iguru.</s></f>"},{ID:137,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato akimoria atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:138,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nyambithie Muthamaki wanyu?</s></f>"},{ID:139,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao Athinjiri-Ngai aria anene magicokia,</s></f>"},{ID:140,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tutiri na Muthamaki ithui, tiga o Kaisari.</s></f>"},{ID:141,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondu ucio akimanengera we akaambwo muti iguru. </s></f>"},{ID:142,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Magikinyita Yesu nake akiumagara ekuuiire muti </s></f>"},{ID:143,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wake, agikinya haria hetaguo handu ha kibuuri, </s></f>"},{ID:144,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>noho hetagwo na Kihibirania Gologotha; na </s></f>"},{ID:145,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hau makimwamba muti iguru, na makiamba andu </s></f>"},{ID:146,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>angi eri miti iguru hamwe nake, umwe mwena uyu na </s></f>"},{ID:147,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>umwe mwena uyu ungi, na yesu e gatagati. Ningi </s></f>"},{ID:148,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Pilato akiandikithia uhoro wake kahengere-ini, </s></f>"},{ID:149,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agigekerithia muti wake iguru. Na uria kaandikituo ni uu:</s></f>"},{ID:150,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>YESU MUNAZARI, MUTHAMAKI WA AYAHUDI</s></f>"},{ID:151,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nao Ayahudi magigithoma uhoro ucio aingi, </s></f>"},{ID:152,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni gukoruo handu hau Yesu aambiruo haari </s></f>"},{ID:153,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hakuhi na ituura; na waandikituo na </s></f>"},{ID:154,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kihibirania, na Kilatini, na Kigiriki. Nao Athinjiri-Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:155,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>aria anene a Ayahudi magikiira Pilato atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:156,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tiga kwandika, Muthamaki wa Ayahudi; </s></f>"},{ID:157,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>andika ati ni kuuga oigire, nii ni nii Muthamaki wa Ayahudi.</s></f>"},{ID:158,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Pilato agicokia atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:159,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uguo ndaandika-ri, ni  ndaandika ndanina.</s></f>"},{ID:160,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nacio thigari, ciarikia kuamba Yesu muti iguru, </s></f>"},{ID:161,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>igikioya nguo ciake,  igicitua maringa mana, </s></f>"},{ID:162,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>muthigari iringa riake, muthigari iringa riake: ona </s></f>"},{ID:163,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kanju nayo makimioya; na riri, kanju iyo ndiari  na </s></f>"},{ID:164,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>rutumo, yarutitio yarutitio iguru gutumwo iri o tama </s></f>"},{ID:165,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>umwe ugwataine mbari ciothe. Tondu ucio </s></f>"},{ID:166,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>magikiirana atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:167,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni tutige kumiatura, tumicukire miti, tumenye </s></f>"},{ID:168,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uria uguthii nayo.</s></f>"},{ID:169,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na ni getha uhoro uria wandikitwo uhingio, </s></f>"},{ID:170,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uria uugite atiri: makigayana nguo ciakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:171,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nario itonyo riakwa makiricukira miti. Uguo </s></f>"},{ID:172,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>noguo thigari ciekire. Na riri, hau muti-ini wa Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:173,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni haarungii nyina, na mwari wa nyina na nyina, </s></f>"},{ID:174,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maria mutumia wa Kileopa, na Maria Magidalena. </s></f>"},{ID:175,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Yesu aakiona nyina, na murutwo uria endete, </s></f>"},{ID:176,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>marungii ho akira nyina atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:177,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mutumia uyu, muruguo ni ucio.</s></f>"},{ID:178,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Agicoka akiira murutwo ucio atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:179,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni ucio nyukwa!</s></f>"},{ID:180,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na gwata o hindi murutwo ucio akimutwara agaature gwake. </s></f>"},{ID:181,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri ringi, amenya ati riu maundu mothe ni mariku, </s></f>"},{ID:182,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni getha uhoro uria mwandike urikie gwikika, </s></f>"},{ID:183,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Yesu akiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:184,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni nyotii.</s></f>"},{ID:185,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uhoro ni warika!</s></f>"},{ID:186,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na haari na nyanja yaigitwo ho iiyuire thiki, </s></f>"},{ID:187,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>magigithecerera ruthanju rua muthobi thibonji iiyuire </s></f>"},{ID:188,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>thiki, makimutwaaririra kanua-ini. Nake Yesu arikia </s></f>"},{ID:189,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>gukunda thiki io agikuaga atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:190,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Uhoro ni warika!</s></f>"},{ID:191,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na akiinamia mutwe agituikana. Ningi tundu ni </s></f>"},{ID:192,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>muthenya wa ihaariria, ciimba itigatinde miti uguru, </s></f>"},{ID:193,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>muthenya wa Thabatu (tondu muthenya ucio waari Thabatu </s></f>"},{ID:194,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>iria nene), Ayahudi  magikihoya Pilato oige andu acio aambe </s></f>"},{ID:195,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>moinwo maguru, ciimba irutwo cieherio. Thigari igigithii </s></f>"},{ID:196,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ikiunanga uria waari wa mbere maguru, o na uria uungi </s></f>"},{ID:197,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maambitwo nake; no maakinya hari Yesu, mona ni arikitie </s></f>"},{ID:198,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>gukua, magitiga kuuna maguru make; no ningi, muthigari umwe </s></f>"},{ID:199,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akimutheca na itimu mbaru, nake, o aathecwo akiura </s></f>"},{ID:200,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>thakame na maai. Na uria wonire ugwo niwe muira, naguo </s></f>"},{ID:201,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uira wake ni wa ma; nake nii oi ma ekuuga, ni getha ona inyui </s></f>"},{ID:202,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mwitikie. Amu-ri, gwekiruo uguo ni getha uhoro uhingio, uria </s></f>"},{ID:203,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>waandikitwo ati, ndari ihindi o na rimwe angiunwo. Na ningi </s></f>"},{ID:204,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uhoro ungi ukaandikwo atiri: makarora uria mathecire. Na </s></f>"},{ID:205,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>thutha ucio  Josebu, wa kuria gwitagwo Arimathea, nake aari </s></f>"},{ID:206,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>murutwo wa Yesu, no ni kuhitha aahithaga ni undu wa gwitigira </s></f>"},{ID:207,
