Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>autware; nake Pilato akimuhe rutha. Agigithii agitwara mwiri wake. </s></f>"},{ID:209,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>O na Nikodemo nake agithii, o uria waambite guthii, </s></f>"},{ID:210,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o uria waambite guthii kuri we utuku, agitwara ndukanio ya </s></f>"},{ID:211,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>manemane na thubiri ingikinya ta ratiri igana. magigitwara mwiri wa Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:212,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>makiuthaya na matama ma gatani o hamwe na minyamu io minungi wega, </s></f>"},{ID:213,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ta mutugo wa Ayahudi wa guthikana. </s></f>"},{ID:214,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na riri, hau aambiruo muti iguru haari mugunda ucio thiini hakagia </s></f>"},{ID:215,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na muungu wa guthikana, mweru, utari waiguo mundu. Handu hau-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:216,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>tondu wa muthenya ucio wa ihaariria ria Ayahudi (amu muungu </s></f>"},{ID:217,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ucio wari hakuhi) niho maakiigire Yesu.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
